<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>等待审批 — WeMonitor</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="pending-body">
  <div class="pending-card">
    <div class="pending-icon">
      <i data-lucide="hourglass" class="icon-xl"></i>
    </div>
    <h2>等待管理员审批</h2>
    <p>您的账号 <strong><%= session.username %></strong> 已注册成功，需要超级管理员审批后才能使用。</p>
    <p class="pending-hint">请联系管理员开通权限。</p>
    <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-secondary">返回登录</a>
  </div>

  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest" defer></script>
  <script>
    if (typeof lucide !== 'undefined') lucide.createIcons();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
